Marne Wale Hai Is A
Universal Truth.

But Yeh Nahi malum Kab.
Agar Yeh Malum rheta
tho Zindagi Paiso ka
hisab Nahi rhakti.
Rhakti tho sirf har Ek
Pal ka hisab.
